"""

`create_dict(::LabeledArray)`

Create a nested `Dict` from a `LabeledArray`.

##### Examples

```julia
julia> t = larr(a=[1 2;3 4], axis1=[:x,:y], axis2=["A","B"])
2 x 2 LabeledArray

  |  |A B
--+--+----
x |a |1 2
